Since then I have been in several raids and am now 52 when I next went in, we were prepared, the plan was good, and I was much better at grps (being a nearly solo 1-50 chanter). We all moved to the succor point withing the zone nvis grp by grp and ended with 2 mobs (which i charmed onto one another while the raid organised). 
<br />
Then the puller brought back 2 fetid fiends and the ireblind; instantly i threw out my aoe which was resisted by the ireblind. A direct mez had the same effect as did charm for a blue con mob; I called the tank to switch target and mezzed the half dead fiend while they destroyed the imp then that dammed enraged spawned. 
<br />
For a 46-55 zone the enraged wasn't touchable by anything. It's aoe brought nmore adds than i can count and i died in seconds. Thankfully i have DoN. 
<br />
Which Dev decided lets put an uber mob in fear and make it nearly impossible for anyone to get there epic drop without a team of 65s plus to kill it needs therapy. put it in an instanced fear or something. 
<br />
My epic is on hold now and i can't see me doing it pre 65...Grrrrr</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
