Basically, since we figured out he was glued to his spawn point and assist agro we have very loudly told our raid members that when he spawns I will spam the raid with a move message and they are to all move south/east along the wall to me immediately.  If pet engages the enraged and they don't have pet hold, they kill their pets.  No exceptions.
